Description: Construct and analyse indexes in a pipeline tidy workflow.
        'tidyindex' contains modules for transforming variables,
        aggregating variables across time, reducing data dimension
        through weighting, and fitting distributions. A manuscript
        describing the methodology can be found at
        <https://github.com/huizezhang-sherry/paper-tidyindex>.
